Package: climateeng
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Tools to Calculate Climatic Comfort Related Parameters
Date: 2016-05-12
Authors@R: c(person("Christoffer", "Rasmussen", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "christofferrasmussen.1987@gmail.com"))
Author: Christoffer Rasmussen [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Christoffer Rasmussen <christofferrasmussen.1987@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/chrras/climateeng
