Description: This package implements P. Ole Fangers thermal comfort indices PMV (Predicted Mean Vote) and PPD (Predicted Percentage Dissatisfied). The package is build on the BASIC code provided in ASHRAE 55-2010. The PMV and PPD functions are capable of handling single values as well as vector input.
